response: Why adopt internationally? There are over 140 million orphans at risk of death due to unclean water or malnutrition, at risk of death due to insufficient or no shelter, at risk of having no education or economic opportunity, at risk of disease, even death by preventable disease, at greater risk of sex trafficking, at risk of being conscripted as child soldiers, and at risk of being conscripted for child labor. Want to hear more?
